rich_message.text: You were the ones who promised that this year’s tuition fees would not increase. But instead of honoring that promise, you did the exact opposite. We are here today because we demand transparency. We demand fairness. We demand accountability.

FEU implemented hybrid classes this year — a mix of online and limited face-to-face sessions. This naturally reduces the use of on-campus facilities and resources. Yet, despite this cutback in physical classes, the tuition fees were increased.
This is not just unfair — it is unacceptable.
So we ask you again, FEU — where is the accountability?

message.text:
WE WANT ACCOUNTABILITY! 
To the FEU administrators:

You were the ones who promised that this year’s tuition fees would not increase. But instead of honoring that promise, you did the exact opposite. We are here today because we demand transparency. We demand fairness. We demand accountability.

Let’s talk about the facts.

FEU implemented hybrid classes this year — a mix of online and limited face-to-face sessions. This naturally reduces the use of on-campus facilities and resources. Yet, despite this cutback in physical classes, the tuition fees were increased.

How does that make sense? 

Less face-to-face learning.

Less access to campus resources.

And still, higher fees?

This is not just unfair — it is unacceptable.

So we ask you again, FEU — where is the accountability?

Where is the consideration for the students and families who trusted your word?

Where is the transparency in your decision-making?

We are not just numbers. We are students. And we deserve better.

message.text:
𝑻𝒐𝒈𝒆𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒓, 𝒘𝒆 𝒔𝒉𝒂𝒑𝒆 𝒕𝒐𝒎𝒐𝒓𝒓𝒐𝒘’𝒔 𝒕𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 🌍

On World Tourism Day, PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter embraces the theme “𝑬𝒎𝒑𝒐𝒘𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑽𝒐𝒍𝒖𝒏𝒕𝒆𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒂 𝑻𝒓𝒂𝒏𝒔𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒗𝒆 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑭𝒖𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆.”

This September, let us celebrate the role of service, unity, and passion in shaping tourism that goes beyond travel—an industry that transforms lives, fosters sustainability, and builds brighter tomorrows.

Because when we serve together, we create a future worth traveling for.

Caption by: Axel Ross
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

#PATAPHFEU

𝑻𝒐𝒈𝒆𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒓, 𝒘𝒆 𝒔𝒉𝒂𝒑𝒆 𝒕𝒐𝒎𝒐𝒓𝒓𝒐𝒘’𝒔 𝒕𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 🌍

On World Tourism Day, PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter embraces the theme “𝑬𝒎𝒑𝒐𝒘𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑽𝒐𝒍𝒖𝒏𝒕𝒆𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒂 𝑻𝒓𝒂𝒏𝒔𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒗𝒆 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑭𝒖𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆.”

This September, let us celebrate the role of service, unity, and passion in shaping tourism that goes beyond travel—an industry that transforms lives, fosters sustainability, and builds brighter tomorrows.

Because when we serve together, we create a future worth traveling for.

Caption by: Axel Ross
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia

On World Tourism Day, PATA Philippines FEU Student Chapter embraces the theme “𝑬𝒎𝒑𝒐𝒘𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝑽𝒐𝒍𝒖𝒏𝒕𝒆𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒂 𝑻𝒓𝒂𝒏𝒔𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒗𝒆 𝑻𝒐𝒖𝒓𝒊𝒔𝒎 𝑭𝒖𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆.”

This September, let us celebrate the role of service, unity, and passion in shaping tourism that goes beyond travel—an industry that transforms lives, fosters sustainability, and builds brighter tomorrows.

Because when we serve together, we create a future worth traveling for.

Caption by: Axel Ross
Pubmat by: Layza Tolomia
